Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.190 --> 00:00:01.810
Here is your next challenge.

00:00:01.810 --> 00:00:05.850
In this Rock Paper Scissors App,
the user selects from three buttons.

00:00:05.850 --> 00:00:09.090
Then, a view is selected with a response
from their opponent, the phone,

00:00:09.090 --> 00:00:10.940
and a win, or lose message.

00:00:10.940 --> 00:00:14.130
Your challenge is to present the results
Results of a match in three different,

00:00:14.130 --> 00:00:16.750
a different way for
each of the three buttons.

00:00:16.750 --> 00:00:20.250
Implement presentation of the results
of your controller from the rock button

00:00:20.250 --> 00:00:21.510
programatically.

00:00:21.510 --> 00:00:25.380
Implement the paper button using
a combination of code and segue.

00:00:25.380 --> 00:00:28.265
And implement the scissors
button using only storyboard,

00:00:28.265 --> 00:00:31.210
apart from the prepare for
segue method of course.

